<div type="definition">
<p>PRODUCE IRON TOOLS.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for forging something by the use of a hammer is duàn 段／鍛.</p>
<p>NB: For liàn 煉 "melt, smelt" see MELT.</p>
        </div>
